node.text:
What an amazing season of @nbcthevoice 🙌🏼 I am beyond grateful for another opportunity to work with incredible artists. Hope you guys enjoyed the “Best of You” duet with @RachelMac and thank you to the @foofighters for letting us perform such a special song for #TheVoice. 

Thank you to everyone on #TeamNick and the @NBCTheVoice team for making this a fantastic season that I’ll never forget!

#BestOfYou is now available on all your favorite streaming platforms 🙌🏼

node.text: #RememberThis is special because it celebrates all the amazing memories we’ve made together, can’t wait to make some more. Thank you guys for helping us put together this video!!

node.text:
Have you heard of time in range? It’s an important measurement for people with diabetes like me, but nearly half don’t know what it is or how it can help.*​​
​
That’s why I’m partnering with @dexcom, @beyondtype1 and other diabetes nonprofits to launch the Global Movement for time in range. Help spread the word by sharing how much better you feel #WhenInRange. #ad ​
​
*Dexcom, U.S. data on file, November 2020
